reviewText: Very good anime, it drags on through the whole thing, but overall I would say it is worth atleast one watch if not more.

The travelers arrive in a world that they have seen before. They left the world in peace before, but things are different now. They must restore  what has been lost. They have solved many problems and saved many people on their journey, but the worst is yet to come. The feather king has his sights set on Sakura. He possesses a multitude of feathers, and he has decided to get rid of Shaoran and protect Sakura himself. There may not be anything that the heroes can do this time.
